OL,3,CSwinney urges 'Westminster reset' on
OL,4,Cchild poverty action
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister has urged
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer to commit to a
OL,8,F"Westminster reset" on child poverty.
OL,10,FJohn Swinney made eradicating child
OL,11,Fpoverty his key target when he first
OL,12,Ftook over the job last month.
OL,14,FIn the second full week of the General
OL,15,FElection campaign, the First Minister
OL,16,Fdeclared the Tories "finished" as he
OL,17,Furged the Labour leader to meet with
OL,18,Fhim to discuss their "shared goals" in
OL,19,Fridding the UK of child poverty
OL,20,Ffollowing an invitation last month.
