OL,3,CSwinney urges 'Westminster reset' on
OL,4,Cchild poverty action
OL,6,F"Eradicating child poverty is my
OL,7,FGovernment's defining mission," the
OL,8,FFirst Minister said.
OL,10,F"The SNP has a proud record of action
OL,11,F` with transformative policies like
OL,12,Fthe baby box, free school meals, free
OL,13,Fbus travel for under-22s and the game-
OL,14,Fchanging Scottish child payment, which
OL,15,Fis contributing to keeping 100,000
OL,16,Fchildren out of poverty in 2024/25.
OL,18,F"The Tories are finished, so Labour
OL,19,Fhas an opportunity to deliver a
OL,20,FWestminster reset on tackling child
OL,21,Fpoverty. They now need to commit to it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]rD@AOUzD@AOU
