OL,3,CSwinney urges 'Westminster reset' on
OL,4,Cchild poverty action
OL,6,F"Once again, I call on Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer to meet with me to discuss our
OL,8,Fshared goals and values on the issue
OL,9,Fof child poverty."
OL,11,FShirley-Anne Somerville ` Scotland's
OL,12,FSocial Justice Secretary ` said the 14
OL,13,Fyears of Conservative-led governments
OL,14,Fat Westminster had "made the Scottish
OL,15,FGovernment's job far more difficult",
OL,16,Fadding: "Sir Keir Starmer's messaging
OL,17,Fhas not been any more assuring.
