OL,3,CSwinney urges 'Westminster reset' on
OL,4,Cchild poverty action
OL,6,F"Hundreds of millions in funding that
OL,7,Fcould have been used for tackling
OL,8,Fpoverty has been handed back unspent
OL,9,Fto the EU by the SNP.
OL,11,F"While the SNP take pot shots at the
OL,12,Fonly party able to kick out the Tories
OL,13,Fand tackle child poverty, Labour is
OL,14,Fcommitted to making work pay, raising
OL,15,Fliving standards and delivering the
OL,16,Fchange we need."
OL,18,FThe Scottish Tories have been
OL,19,Fcontacted for comment.
